 "headingtext_21b5gd5xw24_html": "A family business, a family of butchers, this is the MLS story",
 "textcontent_3nlvekemwyx_html": "Founded in 2008, MLS is one of Oman's leading procurers, processors, and marketers of premium quality red meat.",
 "headingtext_mgaxfv5uwz9_html": "WE EXIST TO NOURISH PEOPLE WITH NATURE'S FINEST RED MEAT.",
 "headingtext_rqm4dre8k5e_html": "WE EXIST TO NOURISH PEOPLE WITH NATURE'S FINEST RED MEAT.",
 "headingtext_5wlpgh77gt5_html": "WE EXIST TO NOURISH PEOPLE WITH NATURE'S FINEST RED MEAT.",
 "headingtext_2bf54vyxcm2_html": "WE EXIST TO NOURISH PEOPLE WITH NATURE'S FINEST RED MEAT.",
 "headingtext_cx9c8vlewgi_html": "<font color=\"#ffffff\">Expanding from Oman to UAE: <\/font><font color=\"#db888b\">A Butchery Legacy<\/font>",
 "textcontent_bk801r4q21h_html": "<font color=\"#ffffff\">MLS is more than just a meat provider; it's a family tradition rooted in butchery expertise for over 45 years. Started in Oman, we're excited to extend our legacy to the UAE. With decades of experience behind us, we're dedicated to delivering top-quality meat products to your doorstep in Dubai within the same day.<\/font>",
 "headingtext_lch5amahtm_html": "Our Journey: A Family Legacy",
 "textcontent_qhl3mk8ixmf_html": "Our story began with Abdul Majid, who laid the foundation for our butchery business in Oman in 1977. His son, Naveed Ahmed, continued the tradition by founding Muscat Livestock in 2008, marking the beginning of a new chapter. Despite challenges like COVID-19, we adapted and thrived, transforming into a successful e-commerce platform in Oman. Now, under the guidance of brothers Naveed &amp; Nadeem Ahmed, we're expanding into the UAE, with over 15 MLS Gourmet stores in Oman paving the way. \u2028",
