 "timeline_title4_jvaz5qepkh_html": "2024",
 "timeline_content4_jvaz5qepkh_html": "<div><b>UAE<\/b><br><\/div>Expanding from Oman to UAE<div><b><br><\/b><\/div>",
 "headingtext_b1vi9mn25tq_html": "Our Mission:&nbsp;<div><font color=\"#f2b2b2\">Quality and Tradition<\/font><\/div>",
 "textcontent_2dy2g3m0or1_html": "At MLS, we're committed to delivering the best. Our goal is simple: to provide ethically sourced, high-quality red meat products. Whether it's hormone-free, antibiotic-free, or grain-fed, we ensure that every product reflects our values of sustainability and excellence. Join us as we bring the taste of tradition to the Oman, one cut at a time."
